          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1652182312905-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1652182312905-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks (reserve some leaves for garnish!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652182321403-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652182321403-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652182321403-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652182321403-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1652182321403-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>in a large bowl with the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>carrot & coriander salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652182319128-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652182319128-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652182319128-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652182319128-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1652182319128-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the top off your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> and hollow out the middle with a spoon</p><p>Tip: Save the removed middle to make breadcrumbs for another recipe!</p><p>Place the <strong>hollowed ciabatta base[s] </strong>and <strong>ciabatta lid[s] </strong>on a baking tray and put in the oven for 5 min or until hot and toasted</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1652182324636-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1652182324636-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1652182324636-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1652182324636-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1652182324636-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken curry </strong>inside the<strong> toasted ciabatta base</strong>,<strong> </strong>top with the <strong>toasted ciabatta lid</strong> and serve the <strong>carrot & coriander salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
